{
  "stem": "17337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 276.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, the ghetto was smaller and smaller and smaller, less and less people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by that time when they started to liquidate, little by little, the ghettos, I was already in Klaj.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that place, they built barracks from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to stay there overnight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they used to-- you see, that Judenrat, you know, they're what the-- the-- the-- the people who are the-- the heads of the-- of the ghetto, they got orders from the German, by tomorrow, you have to bring in 10,000 Jews or 5,000 or whatever.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had to-- to-- to bring that people to a certain place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent them away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was 10,000 people less in the ghetto, because in the ghetto, was a lot of people, a lot of Jews, because they were brought, you know, from the surrounding vicinities, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were small towns, a lot of small towns around Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they all were brought into the ghetto in Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every time after they send away in the ghetto was smaller and smaller, in other words, less and less people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember even when my mother and my sister, she was sent out, I think, with the third one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my uncle still left in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was still in the ghetto because he was working for the-- for the Germans in a fur business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the Germany needed fur, you know, for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was that time already in Klaj.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when it came the last-- last what they called an [GERMAN], you know-- in German, they call it [GERMAN], last transport-- that time they liquidated completely the-- the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no more ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
